data.description: BIG PRICE REDUCTION!! You have Arrived. Welcome to this highly upgraded single story cul de sac home in the heart of the San Diego Country Estates in the city of Ramona. This community is known for its low property taxes and a feature-rich HOA provides budget-friendly fun. Amenities like horse riding trails, pools, jacuzzi/spa, and walking/biking paths offer diverse recreational opportunities without extra expenses. This beautiful home offers tons of privacy on a nearly half acre lot with plenty of mature landscaping and trees all around the property. As you step inside, you will be welcomed in by the brand new LVP flooring that was just installed in September creating a modern and inviting atmosphere. As you explore, you'll discover a spacious living room featuring a large brick fireplace and an open concept floor plan that promotes a warm ambiance. The heart of this home lies in its open kitchen, equipped with all stainless steel appliances, including a convenient wine fridge located where the dishwasher was originally placed. Worried about the dishwasher? Don't be! It's included and ready for use in the garage. The kitchen is not only functional but also aesthetically pleasing, making it a perfect spot for family gatherings. Additionally, this home offers the comfort of a recently replaced water heater, ensuring efficient and reliable hot water supply for your daily needs. Finally down the hallway, you'll find the master suite, providing a private retreat within the home. The thoughtful layout and modern upgrades make this home a comfortable getaway for anyone seeking contemporary living. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this home yours. This one won’t last long!
